Create LoginController with base Endpoint /auth
and additional:
/sign-in
/sign-up

TokenService
 -validateJWT(jwt)
 -generateJWT(userId)


PasswordService
 - encryptPassword(password)
 - validatePassword(unverifiedPassword, validPassword)

Create AuthService with next methods And all needed DTO:
login - will call UserService to get User with password from DB by email and generate JWT Token
        by TokenService.generateJWT(userId)

register - will call UserService to create User after that call TokenService.generateJWT(userId)
            to grand JWT Token fro recently registered User




